  "content": "Design.<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-cyan\">Structure.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    This is where I learn. Trade-offs, judgment calls, and decisions that Claude can't make alone.\n  </div>\n  <!-- Flow -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;\">\n    <div class=\"flow-step\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-amber);\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 28px;\">&#129300;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">Explore the Problem</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">Brainstorm approaches with Claude. Pull in latest research. Compare alternatives.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flow-arrow\">&#8595;</div>\n    <div class=\"flow-step\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-blue);\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 28px;\">&#128196;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">Write the RFC</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">Document the chosen approach. Decisions, trade-offs, rejected alternatives.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flow-arrow\">&#8595;</div>\n    <div class=\"flow-step\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-purple);\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 28px;\">&#128269;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">5-Persona Review on the Design</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">SWE, PM, QA + dynamic reviewers validate the spec before any code.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flow-arrow\">&#8595;</div>\n    <div class=\"flow-step\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-green);\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 28px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">Generate Structured Issues</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">Dependency graphs, phases, acceptance criteria, tracking issues.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>",
